ygData.messageBody:
Wurmslayers are actually not that great of a
weapon. They are extreamly heavy and pretty slow, in my
opinion the high damage is not worth it. This is my take
on it after using a wurmslayer for about 10
levels.<br>My level 39 Ranger is using a Centi Longsword in
secondary and Crystaline Short Sword in Primary. I don't
really like the CSS, but I love the Centi Longsword...
For level 35 I fought in Overthere and The Great
Divide, but now with Luclin, there could be a better
place for you.<br>Good Luck!!<br>~Siai<br>45
Druid<br>~Atrana<br>40 Warrior<br>~Twara<br>39 Ranger<br>~*~SARYRN~*~
